a.wong%2Fvideos%2F10155479180184567%2F&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=c7781c7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/teea.wong/videos/10155479180184567/</a><br />\n<br />\n23:45 港鐵再次不停元朗站<br />\n<br />\n其他片段:<br />\n白衫人警察面前行過一個都唔拉<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chicharito.kobe.awy0.0/videos/10217697781769215/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchicharito.kobe.awy0.0%2Fvideos%2F10217697781769215%2F&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=e00440ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chicharito.kobe.awy0.0/videos/10217697781769215/</a><br />\n<br />\n督察話唔答記者問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wusiuwu/videos/10162072219475035/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwusiuwu%2Fvideos%2F10162072219475035%2F&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=76a26694\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wusiuwu/videos/10162072219475035/</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗第二次打人，白衫人爆鐵柵<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/muddydirtywater/videos/346595906239943/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmuddydirtywater%2Fvideos%2F346595906239943%2F&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=b2412ed7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/muddydirtywater/videos/346595906239943/</a><br />\n<br />\n何君堯受盡元朗白衫人士歡迎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1111790042339586/posts/1135639439954646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1111790042339586%2Fposts%2F1135639439954646&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=4fd82a07\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1111790042339586/posts/1135639439954646</a><br />\n<br />\n觀迎巴絲更新及指正<br />\n<br />\n及本人意見:<br />\n我地唔可以比手足同無辜市民白白犠牲，要推盡文宣打贏輿論<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 唔可以比黑警(主要)同政府同呢班暴徒割蓆，要做到 &quot;警黑合作，警黑一家親&quot;</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 藍營一定會spin 今次係我地呢面自導自演，深藍一定會深信(佢地只會相信佢地肯相信的事)，我地目標係要淺籃同中立知道藍營幾咁黑暗，要佢地企我地呢面</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n希望各大文宣組同鍵戰盡做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97af72e5aa80ac96fea00a4c75165f339d7c1870","tid":1343321,"uid":258270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:45:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"176b527274080a2b0580ec7f61793867423b6f8e","tid":1343321,"uid":258270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:56:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"05f2a0bdbdc3692be5da3b233aa52bf4968e78b6","tid":1343321,"uid":258270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:05:46.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}